    // Page Navigation

    function navigateTo(page) {

      // Store the previous page before navigating

      if (currentPage !== page) {

        lastPage = currentPage;

      }

     

      // Get the main scrollable container

      const mainContainer = document.querySelector('main');

     

      // Force scroll to top using ALL available methods

      window.scrollTo({top: 0, left: 0, behavior: 'instant'});

      document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0;

      document.body.scrollTop = 0;

      if (mainContainer) {

        mainContainer.scrollTop = 0;

      }

     

      // Hide all pages

      document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));

     

      // Show selected page

      document.getElementById(`page-${page}`).classList.add('active');

      currentPage = page;

     

      // Force scroll to top again multiple times with different timings

      requestAnimationFrame(() => {

        window.scrollTo({top: 0, left: 0, behavior: 'instant'});

        document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0;

        document.body.scrollTop = 0;

        if (mainContainer) {

          mainContainer.scrollTop = 0;

        }

      });

     

      setTimeout(() => {

        window.scrollTo({top: 0, left: 0, behavior: 'instant'});

        document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0;

        document.body.scrollTop = 0;

        if (mainContainer) {

          mainContainer.scrollTop = 0;

        }

      }, 0);

     

      setTimeout(() => {

        window.scrollTo({top: 0, left: 0, behavior: 'instant'});

        document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0;

        document.body.scrollTop = 0;

        if (mainContainer) {

          mainContainer.scrollTop = 0;

        }

      }, 50);

     

      setTimeout(() => {

        window.scrollTo({top: 0, left: 0, behavior: 'instant'});

        document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0;

        document.body.scrollTop = 0;

        if (mainContainer) {

          mainContainer.scrollTop = 0;

        }

      }, 100);

     

      // If navigating to websites page, render websites

      if (page === 'websites') {

        renderWebsites();

        renderCategories();

      }

    }

    // Setup infinite scroll

    function setupInfiniteScroll() {

      const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {

        entries.forEach(entry => {

          if (entry.isIntersecting && !isLoadingHomeWebsites && !allHomeWebsitesLoaded && currentPage === 'home') {

            loadMoreHomeWebsites();

          }

        });

      }, {

        rootMargin: '100px'

      });

      const loadingIndicator = document.getElementById('home-loading');

      if (loadingIndicator) {

        observer.observe(loadingIndicator);

      }

    }

    // Load more websites

    function loadMoreHomeWebsites() {

      if (isLoadingHomeWebsites || allHomeWebsitesLoaded) return;

      isLoadingHomeWebsites = true;

      document.getElementById('home-loading').classList.remove('hidden');

      // Simulate loading delay

      setTimeout(() => {

        renderHomeWebsites();

        isLoadingHomeWebsites = false;

       

        if (!allHomeWebsitesLoaded) {

          document.getElementById('home-loading').classList.add('hidden');

        } else {

          document.getElementById('home-loading').classList.add('hidden');

        }

      }, 800);

    }

        dot.className = `w-3 h-3 rounded-full transition ${index === 0 ? 'bg-white' : 'bg-white/50'}`;

        heroDots.appendChild(dot);

      });

    }

    // Hero carousel controls

    let heroCarouselInterval;

    let currentHeroIndex = 0;

    function startHeroCarouselAutoplay() {

      heroCarouselInterval = setInterval(() => {

        currentHeroIndex = (currentHeroIndex + 1) % 5;

        scrollHeroCarousel(currentHeroIndex);

      }, 5000);

    }

    function scrollHeroCarousel(index) {

      const carousel = document.getElementById('hero-carousel');

      const dots = document.getElementById('hero-dots').children;

      carousel.scrollLeft = carousel.offsetWidth * index;

      currentHeroIndex = index;

     

      Array.from(dots).forEach((dot, i) => {

        dot.className = `w-3 h-3 rounded-full transition ${i === index ? 'bg-white' : 'bg-white/50'}`;

      });

      clearInterval(heroCarouselInterval);

      startHeroCarouselAutoplay();

    }

    document.getElementById('hero-prev')?.addEventListener('click', () => {

      currentHeroIndex = (currentHeroIndex - 1 + 5) % 5;

      scrollHeroCarousel(currentHeroIndex);

    });

    document.getElementById('hero-next')?.addEventListener('click', () => {

      currentHeroIndex = (currentHeroIndex + 1) % 5;

      scrollHeroCarousel(currentHeroIndex);

    });

    // Render categories

    function renderCategories() {

      const container = document.getElementById('category-chips');

      if (!container) return;

     

      container.innerHTML = '';

     

      categories.forEach(cat => {

        const chip = document.createElement('button');

        chip.className = `px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition btn-press shadow-sm ${

          currentFilter === cat

            ? 'bg-purple-600 text-white'

            : 'bg-white text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100'

        }`;

        chip.textContent = cat;

        chip.onclick = () => filterByCategory(cat);

        container.appendChild(chip);

      });

    }

    // Filter websites

    function filterByCategory(category) {

      currentFilter = category;

      if (currentPage === 'websites') {

        renderCategories();

        renderWebsites();

      }

    }

    // Search functionality

    let searchTimeout;

    document.getElementById('search-input')?.addEventListener('input', (e) => {

      clearTimeout(searchTimeout);

      searchTimeout = setTimeout(() => {

        searchQuery = e.target.value.toLowerCase();

        if (currentPage === 'websites') {

          renderWebsites();

        }

      }, 300);

    });

    function changeMainImage(imgSrc, index) {

      document.getElementById('detail-main-image').src = imgSrc;

      const thumbnails = document.querySelectorAll('#detail-thumbnails > div');

      thumbnails.forEach((thumb, i) => {

    // Image zoom functions

    function openImageZoom(images, startIndex = 0) {

      currentZoomImages = images;

      currentZoomIndex = startIndex;

      updateZoomedImage();

      document.getElementById('image-zoom-modal').classList.remove('hidden');

      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';

    }

    function closeImageZoom() {

      document.getElementById('image-zoom-modal').classList.add('hidden');

      document.body.style.overflow = '';

    }

    function updateZoomedImage() {

      document.getElementById('zoomed-image').src = currentZoomImages[currentZoomIndex];

      document.getElementById('zoom-image-counter').textContent = `${currentZoomIndex + 1} / ${currentZoomImages.length}`;

    }

    function nextZoomedImage() {

      currentZoomIndex = (currentZoomIndex + 1) % currentZoomImages.length;

      updateZoomedImage();

    }

    function previousZoomedImage() {

      currentZoomIndex = (currentZoomIndex - 1 + currentZoomImages.length) % currentZoomImages.length;

      updateZoomedImage();

    }

    // Keyboard navigation for zoom

    document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {

      const zoomModal = document.getElementById('image-zoom-modal');

      if (!zoomModal.classList.contains('hidden')) {

        if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') {

          nextZoomedImage();

        } else if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') {

          previousZoomedImage();

        } else if (e.key === 'Escape') {

          closeImageZoom();

        }

      }

    });

    let lastPage = 'home';

    function navigateBack() {

      // If we're on details page, go back to websites

      if (currentPage === 'details') {

        navigateTo('websites');

      }

      // If we're on terms/privacy/refund and lastPage is set, go back there

      else if (lastPage && lastPage !== currentPage) {

        navigateTo(lastPage);

      }

      // Default to home

      else {

        navigateTo('home');

      }

    }

    // Cart functions

    function addToCart(id) {

      if (!cart.includes(id)) {

        cart.push(id);

        localStorage.setItem('sril_cart', JSON.stringify(cart));

        updateCartCount();

        showToast('Added to cart!', 'success');

      } else {

        showToast('Already in cart', 'info');

      }

    }

    function removeFromCart(id) {

      cart = cart.filter(c => c !== id);

      localStorage.setItem('sril_cart', JSON.stringify(cart));

      updateCartCount();

      renderCartItems();

      showToast('Removed from cart', 'info');

    }

    function updateCartCount() {

      const count = cart.length;

      const badge = document.getElementById('cart-count');

      const mobileBadge = document.getElementById('mobile-cart-count');

     

      if (count > 0) {

        badge.textContent = count;

        badge.classList.remove('hidden');

        mobileBadge.textContent = count;

        mobileBadge.classList.remove('hidden');

      } else {

        badge.classList.add('hidden');

        mobileBadge.classList.add('hidden');

      }

    }

    function openCart() {

      renderCartItems();

      document.getElementById('cart-sidebar').style.transform = 'translateX(0)';

      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';

    }

    function closeCart() {

      document.getElementById('cart-sidebar').style.transform = 'translateX(100%)';

      document.body.style.overflow = '';

    }

    function renderCartItems() {

      const container = document.getElementById('cart-items');

      const emptyState = document.getElementById('cart-empty');

      const footer = document.getElementById('cart-footer');

      if (cart.length === 0) {

        container.classList.add('hidden');

        emptyState.classList.remove('hidden');

        footer.classList.add('hidden');

        return;

      }

      container.classList.remove('hidden');

      emptyState.classList.add('hidden');

      footer.classList.remove('hidden');

     

      // Reset form visibility

      document.getElementById('customer-details-form').classList.add('hidden');

      document.getElementById('checkout-button').classList.remove('hidden');

      document.getElementById('whatsapp-checkout-button').classList.add('hidden');

      const cartWebsites = websites.filter(w => cart.includes(w.id));

     

      container.innerHTML = cartWebsites.map(w => `

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">

          <div class="flex">

            <img src="${w.images[0]}" alt="${w.name}" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-lg object-cover">

            <div class="ml-4 flex-1">

              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-1">

                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-900 bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">${w.productId}</span>

              </div>

              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">${w.name}</h4>

              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">${w.category}</p>

              <button onclick="removeFromCart(${w.id})" class="text-red-600 text-sm hover:text-red-700 transition btn-press">

                Remove

              </button>

            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      `).join('');

      document.getElementById('cart-total-items').textContent = cart.length;

    }

    function checkoutCart() {

      // Validate form

      const form = document.getElementById('cart-customer-form');

      if (!form.checkValidity()) {

        form.reportValidity();

        return;

      }

      if (cart.length === 0) return;

      const name = document.getElementById('cart-name').value;

      const mobile = document.getElementById('cart-mobile').value;

      const email = document.getElementById('cart-email').value;

      const company = document.getElementById('cart-company').value;

      const notes = document.getElementById('cart-notes').value;

      const termsAccepted = document.getElementById('cart-terms').checked;

      if (!termsAccepted) {

        showToast('Please accept the terms and conditions', 'error');

        return;

      }

      const cartWebsites = websites.filter(w => cart.includes(w.id));

      const websiteList = cartWebsites.map((w, i) => `${i + 1}. ${w.productId} - ${w.name} (${w.category})`).join('%0A');

     

      let message = `Hello SRIL,%0A%0A*NEW ORDER REQUEST*%0A%0A`;

      message += `*Customer Details:*%0A`;

      message += `Name: ${encodeURIComponent(name)}%0A`;

      message += `Mobile: ${mobile}%0A`;

      message += `Email: ${encodeURIComponent(email)}%0A`;

      if (company) message += `Company: ${encodeURIComponent(company)}%0A`;

      message += `%0A*Websites Selected:*%0A${websiteList}%0A`;

      if (notes) message += `%0A*Additional Notes:*%0A${encodeURIComponent(notes)}%0A`;

      message += `%0A*Legal Acknowledgment:*%0AI have read and agreed to the Terms & Conditions, Privacy Policy, and Refund Policy.%0A`;

      message += `%0APlease provide pricing and next steps.`;

     

      window.open(`https://wa.me/917799086877?text=${message}`, '_blank', 'noopener,noreferrer');

     

      // Clear form after sending

      form.reset();

      showToast('Redirecting to WhatsApp...', 'success');

    }

    function proceedToCheckout() {

      // Show customer details form

      document.getElementById('customer-details-form').classList.remove('hidden');

      document.getElementById('checkout-button').classList.add('hidden');

      document.getElementById('whatsapp-checkout-button').classList.remove('hidden');

    }

    // Wishlist functions

    function toggleWishlist(id) {

      const index = wishlist.indexOf(id);

      if (index > -1) {

        wishlist.splice(index, 1);

        showToast('Removed from wishlist', 'info');

      } else {

        wishlist.push(id);

        showToast('Added to wishlist!', 'success');

       

        // Heart animation

        const heartBtn = event.currentTarget.querySelector('svg');

        heartBtn.classList.add('heart-animate');

        setTimeout(() => heartBtn.classList.remove('heart-animate'), 500);

      }

     

      localStorage.setItem('sril_wishlist', JSON.stringify(wishlist));

      updateWishlistCount();

     

      if (currentPage === 'websites') {

        renderWebsites();

      }

    }

    function updateWishlistCount() {

      const count = wishlist.length;

      const badge = document.getElementById('wishlist-count');

      const moreWishlistBadge = document.getElementById('more-wishlist-count');

     

      if (count > 0) {

        badge.textContent = count;

        badge.classList.remove('hidden');

        if (moreWishlistBadge) {

          moreWishlistBadge.textContent = count;

          moreWishlistBadge.classList.remove('hidden');

        }

      } else {

        badge.classList.add('hidden');

        if (moreWishlistBadge) {

          moreWishlistBadge.classList.add('hidden');

        }

      }

    }

    // Toast notifications

    function showToast(message, type = 'info') {

      const container = document.getElementById('toast-container');

      const toast = document.createElement('div');

     

      const bgColors = {

        success: 'bg-green-500',

        error: 'bg-red-500',

        info: 'bg-blue-600'

      };

      toast.className = `toast ${bgColors[type]} text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-2`;

      toast.textContent = message;

     

      container.appendChild(toast);

     

      setTimeout(() => {

        toast.style.opacity = '0';

        toast.style.transform = 'translateY(-100%)';

        setTimeout(() => toast.remove(), 300);

      }, 3000);

    }

    // Send details enquiry to WhatsApp

    function sendDetailsEnquiry() {

      if (!currentModalWebsite) return;

      // Validate form

      const form = document.getElementById('details-customer-form');

      if (!form.checkValidity()) {

        form.reportValidity();

        return;

      }

      const name = document.getElementById('details-name').value;

      const mobile = document.getElementById('details-mobile').value;

      const email = document.getElementById('details-email').value;

      const notes = document.getElementById('details-notes').value;

      const termsAccepted = document.getElementById('details-terms').checked;

      if (!termsAccepted) {

        showToast('Please accept the terms and conditions', 'error');

        return;

      }

      let message = `Hello SRIL,%0A%0A*ENQUIRY FOR: ${currentModalWebsite.productId} - ${currentModalWebsite.name}*%0A%0A`;

      message += `*Customer Details:*%0A`;

      message += `Name: ${encodeURIComponent(name)}%0A`;

      message += `Mobile: ${mobile}%0A`;

      message += `Email: ${encodeURIComponent(email)}%0A`;

      message += `%0A*Website:* ${currentModalWebsite.productId} - ${currentModalWebsite.name} (${currentModalWebsite.category})%0A`;

      if (notes) message += `%0A*Message:*%0A${encodeURIComponent(notes)}%0A`;
